1) Checkout project from GitHub
2) Right click on project, Select configure
3) Select convert to maven project
4) Right click on project Do maven clean and install
5) Open com.apartment.management.config.PersistanceJpaConfig.getDataSource() method
6) Update the DB Details
7) Right click on project select Run as Option
8) select "Maven Build" option
9) In Goals add "clean install tomcat7:run"
10)select source and add "workspace"
11) Run the project